---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { defaultPhone, defaultTelHref } from '../data/business';

const phone = defaultPhone;
const telHref = defaultTelHref;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Tyre Emergency Ltd | Dean Spicer, REACT Licensed Mobile Tyre Fitter"
  description="Run by Dean Spicer — two generations in the tyre trade, over a decade full-time, REACT licensed and built around fast-response mobile tyre fitting from Bilsthorpe, Nottinghamshire."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>The person who won&rsquo;t leave you stranded.</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">A sole-operator business run by Dean Spicer from Bilsthorpe, Nottinghamshire. The fitter on the phone is the fitter at your door &mdash; no rota, no agency cover, no handovers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-split">
        <div class="service-split-image">
          <img
            src="/images/dean-tyre-fitter.webp"
            alt="Dean Spicer working at the tyre changer inside his service van"
            width="933"
            height="700"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="service-split-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">The Story</span>
          <h2>Two generations in the tyre trade</h2>
          <p>Dean&rsquo;s dad set up the UK&rsquo;s first mobile tyre service in August 1990, and Dean was on the van at weekends from his teens. Full-time in the trade from age twenty &mdash; fitter, mechanic, manager &mdash; through national chains, independent garages, and helping grow the family business in Dorset into a seven-van fleet.</p>
          <p>Tyre Emergency Ltd was set up in December 2023 after a move up North to buy a house and start a family. The focus is fast-response roadside work &mdash; modern cars rarely come with a spare, and a flat that used to be an inconvenience is now a proper crisis. Hundreds of tyres in stock at the unit, the right one grabbed before the van leaves. When you&rsquo;re stood at the roadside in the rain, the last thing you want is someone still learning. You won&rsquo;t get that here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark video-section">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Watch us work</span>
      <h2>Dean on the tools</h2>
      <p>A clip from his time at Freeway Mobile Tyres in Dorset &mdash; same fitter, same standards, before the move up North.</p>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="yt-facade"
        data-yt-id="czX__fA_3zY"
        aria-label="Play video of Dean fitting a tyre"
      >
        <img
          src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/czX__fA_3zY/maxresdefault.jpg"
          alt=""
          width="1280"
          height="720"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <span class="yt-facade-play" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 68 48" width="68" height="48"><path d="M66.52 7.74c-.78-2.93-2.49-5.41-5.42-6.19C55.79.13 34 0 34 0S12.21.13 6.9 1.55c-2.93.78-4.63 3.26-5.42 6.19C.06 13.05 0 24 0 24s.06 10.95 1.48 16.26c.78 2.93 2.49 5.41 5.42 6.19C12.21 47.87 34 48 34 48s21.79-.13 27.1-1.55c2.93-.78 4.64-3.26 5.42-6.19C67.94 34.95 68 24 68 24s-.06-10.95-1.48-16.26z" fill="#f00"/><path d="M45 24 27 14v20z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
        </span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">REACT Licensing</span>
      <h2>What &ldquo;REACT licensed&rdquo; actually means</h2>
      <p>REACT licensing is about one specific thing: working safely at the roadside. Cones, beacons, vehicle setup, scene assessment &mdash; keeping you, the traffic and the fitter safe with cars passing at speed. It&rsquo;s not a tick-box course &mdash; your van has to meet certain standards and you need real roadside experience before you&rsquo;re even eligible. When we turn up on the M1 hard shoulder or the verge of an A-road at 2am, nobody&rsquo;s improvising.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span>
        <h2>What to expect when you call</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3 values-grid">
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>An exact price on the phone</h3>
          <p>You get an all-in quote before we go anywhere. No call-out fees, no per-mile charges, no VAT added at the end. What you&rsquo;re told is what you pay.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>An ETA that actually means something</h3>
          <p>We give you a realistic ETA based on where we actually are, not a best-case figure to keep you on the call. If something changes, we ring. If we can&rsquo;t reach you fast enough, we say so.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <h3>The right tyre, fitted properly</h3>
          <p>Tyres matched to the vehicle &mdash; correct size, load rating and speed rating &mdash; balanced and torque-wrenched before we leave. Not just slapped on with an impact gun.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="about-availability">
        <strong>One honest note on availability.</strong> The service runs round the clock, but it&rsquo;s a one-man operation &mdash; most of the time the phone gets answered straight away, but there are stretches when Dean&rsquo;s mid-job, asleep between shifts or briefly off the clock. If you don&rsquo;t get through, drop a quick text or try again in a few minutes &mdash; he&rsquo;ll come back as soon as he&rsquo;s free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Philosophy</span>
      <h2>An emergency is a bad enough day already.</h2>
      <p>Most people who call us are stressed &mdash; late for work, late for the airport, sat with the kids in a cold car on an unlit lane. So the call is kept short. We need three things: where you are, what you&rsquo;re driving and what&rsquo;s happened. You get the price and the ETA, you decide. That&rsquo;s the whole service model &mdash; and it&rsquo;s what nearly five hundred Google reviews consistently say back.</p>
      <div class="cta-row about-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href={telHref}>Call {phone}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(900px 500px at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 45, 45, 0.08), transparent 60%);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    max-width: 22ch;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
  }

  /* Body paragraphs across the page: looser, slightly larger,
     line-length capped for comfortable reading. */
  .section .container-narrow p,
  .service-split-content p {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .section .container-narrow p {
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .page-hero-sub {
    color: var(--color-text-muted-dark);
    max-width: 60ch;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .values-grid {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    height: 100%;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted-dark);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .about-availability {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* YouTube facade: thumbnail + play button, replaced with iframe on click */
  .video-section h2,
  .video-section p {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .video-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }
  .video-section .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .yt-facade {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: #000;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }
  .yt-facade:hover,
  .yt-facade:focus-visible {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 22px 48px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
  }
  .yt-facade img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: opacity var(--transition);
  }
  .yt-facade:hover img,
  .yt-facade:focus-visible img {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .yt-facade-play {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45));
    transition: transform var(--transition);
  }
  .yt-facade:hover .yt-facade-play,
  .yt-facade:focus-visible .yt-facade-play {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.05);
  }
  .yt-facade iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
    display: block;
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.yt-facade').forEach((facade) => {
    facade.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const id = facade.dataset.ytId;
      if (!id) return;
      const iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
      iframe.src = `https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/${id}?autoplay=1&rel=0&modestbranding=1`;
      iframe.title = 'Dean fitting a tyre at Freeway Mobile Tyres';
      iframe.allow = 'accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture';
      iframe.allowFullscreen = true;
      facade.replaceWith(iframe);
      // Move classes onto the iframe so it inherits the rounded corners + size.
      iframe.className = 'yt-facade-frame';
      iframe.style.aspectRatio = '16 / 9';
      iframe.style.width = '100%';
      iframe.style.maxWidth = '880px';
      iframe.style.margin = '0 auto';
      iframe.style.display = 'block';
      iframe.style.borderRadius = 'var(--radius)';
      iframe.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    });
  });
</script>
